"The Sparkle In Your Eye"

2
00:00:49,300 --> 00:00:53,300
(Episode 6)

3
00:00:57,440 --> 00:00:59,600
Brother Fang, what did you
need to see me about today?

4
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:14,400
You went to do that restaurant
ribbon-cutting ceremony.

5
00:01:15,160 --> 00:01:16,680
Brother Fang, I'm really sorry.

6
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:18,200
Just wrapped the shoot.

7
00:01:18,240 --> 00:01:20,200
Finished the project,
got a bit carried away.

8
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:25,160
But honestly, the
schedule's been packed solid.

9
00:01:27,600 --> 00:01:29,200
You haven't been to the company in ages.

10
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,760
We just renovated the office recently.

11
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:34,120
