on your current clout.

22
00:01:58,640 --> 00:01:59,560
And fanbase.

23
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:00,600
To make more money.

24
00:02:00,601 --> 00:02:02,000
And secure your position.

25
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:03,600
