34
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:19,200
I need to go.

35
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:40,840
Brother Jia.

36
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:43,160
We'll do the costume
fitting before going shopping.

37
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:44,520
The stylists are already waiting.

38
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:47,160
Three public appearances this afternoon.

39
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:49,160
All outfits are brand-sponsored.

40
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:51,280
Any paparazzi bothering you lately.

41
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:54,240
No, why? Did something happen?

42
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:58,520
Nothing. How many
engagements this afternoon.

43
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:01,280
Three today, three more tomorrow.

44
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:03,440
Tonight, Mr. Fang is meeting a producer.

45
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:05,480
