46
00:03:05,600 --> 00:03:07,120
Exploring collaboration possibilities.

47
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:21,720
Hello.

48
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:23,439
Is this Mr. Su Yi.

49
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:24,800
Are you available for an audition?

50
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:26,960
Hello.

51
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:28,000
Hi.

52
