Nineteen.

59
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,680
No college education.

60
00:03:55,880 --> 00:03:56,880
My first piece is.

61
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:59,800
Untrained actors never work out.

62
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:16,560
Can you come for a callback tomorrow.

63
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,600
Let me check my schedule.

64
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:18,760
Waiter.

65
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:19,800
Coming.

66
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:22,960
Get ice now.

67
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,600
One more mistake and you're fired.

68
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,800
