78
00:05:00,440 --> 00:05:01,000
Cut.
Overact.

79
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,080
OK OK

80
00:05:02,081 --> 00:05:03,520
That was... interesting.

81
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:05,839
- We'll be in touch.
- My later performance gets more nuanced.

82
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:06,640
No problem.
We've seen enough.

83
00:05:07,601 --> 00:05:08,640
