120
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:44,640
Hmm, it is a bit.

121
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:47,879
Bro, why don't you go home first?

122
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:49,320
I'll make you another one tonight.

123
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,000
No need.

124
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,480
How have you been lately?

125
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:54,360
I heard you went to an audition.

126
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,480
