130
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:09,880
Bro.

131
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:11,200
Hmm.

132
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:13,520
I really want to act.

133
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,839
