142
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,160
Remember to take time off.

143
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,480
Okay.

144
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:45,280
Leaving.

145
00:07:45,440 --> 00:07:46,440
Take care, bro.

146
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,600
Take time off.

147
00:07:48,601 --> 00:07:49,961
Still thinking about taking leave.

148
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:51,080
Manager

149
00:07:51,081 --> 00:07:53,080
I'll go borrow ice from
the neighboring bar now.

150
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:53,760
Ah

151
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,800
I'll cover the cost.

152
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,360
You just came back a few days ago.

153
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:58,039
