158
00:08:07,441 --> 00:08:08,599
I don't care who he is.

159
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,560
Our shop is small,

160
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:11,160
can't afford a big Buddha like you.

161
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:16,880
