162
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:18,400
But.

163
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,000
I want to tell you.

164
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:23,560
Even if I imagine myself liking you.

165
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,440
Or forget you later.

166
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:27,960
Every moment

167
00:08:29,400 --> 00:08:30,400
I've loved you.

168
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:33,080
Brother Jia, Mr. Fang
asked if you're free tonight.

169
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,440
No.

170
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,480
