182
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,480
No.

183
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,600
Su Yi.

184
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,680
Should be coming.

185
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,360
Should be coming.

186
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,000
Director.

187
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:32,040
Ah.

188
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,440
